14 WHEREAS, dental hygienists are essential in dental offices, public health facilities, schools,
15 private organizations, and research facilities to provide the best oral health care for all
16 citizens.
17 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE SENATE that the members of this body
18 recognize February 6, 2025, as Dental Hygienists Appreciation Day at the state capitol and
19 encourage our citizens to honor dental hygienists for the vital services they provide in
20 maintaining good oral hygiene and dental health.
21 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Secretary of the Senate is authorized and directed
22 to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to the Georgia Dental
23 Hygienists' Association.
